{
  "texts": [
    "Advanced user educators (21.1%) advocated for a more collaborative approach.",
    "They suggested the implementation of a system in which educators could give feedback on AI-generated responses.",
    "Such an iterative process would serve to refine and improve the AI models continuously, making the models more accurate and relevant for diverse educational contexts.",
    "For non-English-as-a-first-language speakers, this process could be particularly useful in detecting and addressing language errors that automated systems might otherwise overlook.",
    "Having a dedicated AI language model within a controlled sandbox environment addresses the integration issue, as the model can be designed to interact with the existing educational platforms seamlessly and tools utilised within the institution."
  ]
}